snippet.title: Traffic AI I Feature Highlights #2 I Cities: Skylines II
snippet.description:
Why do the citizens of your city make the decisions they do and how does that affect traffic simulation? In today's Feature Highlights, we go over the improved Traffic AI. 🚗 

Read the full Dev Diary HERE! 
https://forum.paradoxplaza.com/forum/developer-diary/development-diary-2-traffic-ai.1591141/

Footage captured In-Game is not final and might change in time for release.
